commit.message: Stricter authorization checks for qrcodes in the admin interface.
Fix Server Error in Admin when opening EmailDevice

Restore raw body template for EmailDevice.

Also various test improvements.

Add throttling to EmailDevice and StaticDevice.

I also pulled the throttling tests into their own mixin so they're easy
to instantiate for new throttled devices.
Allow setting otp_email body template from settings
Add alternative email address field to otp_email
